{"tid":755145,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[鋼琴撚] 點先可以精進自己既琴技","createTime":"2018-07-25T03:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T01:18:04.000Z","uid":193485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"df60b140c74c5701903e026b793e74ae2ce732c9","tid":755145,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"7年前考完8級鋼琴之後就停咗學琴<br />\n呢排彈返 想考ARSM <br />\n但自己彈Chopin啲歌練極都冇乜進展 彈得唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手指唔夠靈活 左右手唔協調 左手直頭係垃圾地笨拙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點先可以好似啲高手咁完美駕馭難度高少少既歌(e.g Chopin, Liszt)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係我資質平庸 基本功唔好 可以收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7284cafaa3d103a27fabcb2ee1502f03a91ac858","tid":755145,"uid":193485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:32:36.000Z","msg":"望住啲所謂既練習曲 我真係得啖笑<br />\n完全唔係我既程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 難到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10639e37ff4351c63480eb9980f427ba1da2368","tid":755145,"uid":117602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:35:29.000Z","msg":"留名學嘢"},{"pid":"10892350262841b293261782b850aabb47093fa9","tid":755145,"uid":193485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"點解8級咁撚易 再上就咁撚難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4262b66eb2b973cfc81b5e7ecc12244efa45a03f","tid":755145,"uid":192485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:36:59.000Z","msg":"不如花時間練習"},{"pid":"6371f4ea62f4dcb57340e73f295fae113967b5c3","tid":755145,"uid":3138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:38:54.000Z","msg":"搵返個老師睇睇啦"},{"pid":"37127f363ddf71f32c649399f803